  "2026-03-04T19:08:10.303Z",cursor-maintainer,"Implemented token-aware recursive test-all detection in src/cli/commands/test.ts for pm, node dist/cli.js, direct dist/cli.js, and npx pm-cli/pm forms with global-flag and env-prefix handling; added regression scenarios in tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts for add-time rejection and runtime skip parity."
